    "description": "我们希望有更多热爱这类型游戏的朋友们可以参与到试玩并给出任何游戏反馈，大家的支持是团队的最大动力！感谢！<br>《旅人竞技场》交流QQ群：670079375<br><br>《旅人竞技场》是一款轻度动作性的Roguelike冒险游戏，背景设定于架空的角斗士世界。玩家将扮演角斗士，在三层竞技场中不断战斗，体验丰富的随机性和重复游玩乐趣。通过突袭系统与敌人交互，利用宝物组合构建专属强力Build，享受成型后横扫战场的爽快感。每一次选择都将影响你的成长路径，挑战极限，成为传奇角斗士！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063190/extras/99e6c68140723acc17f0116895eb9fc5.webp?t=1763218319\" width=615 height=58 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063190/extras/b6e3e0b29afc38b0918af7eec894ced8.poster.avif?t=1763218319\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063190/extras/b6e3e0b29afc38b0918af7eec894ced8.webm?t=1763218319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063190/extras/b6e3e0b29afc38b0918af7eec894ced8.mp4?t=1763218319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>对敌人造成失衡后，可发动冲刺造成大量伤害并击落精力球。拾取精力球能填充绝招能量条，形成连续进攻与资源循环的战斗节奏，操作简单且富有策略性。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063190/extras/dbb2c56d3f505a25dda1daaa4dcce52f.webp?t=1763218319\" width=615 height=58 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063190/extras/a6142c0469357d6b9058d7070ecfdce7.poster.avif?t=1763218319\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063190/extras/a6142c0469357d6b9058d7070ecfdce7.webm?t=1763218319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063190/extras/a6142c0469357d6b9058d7070ecfdce7.mp4?t=1763218319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>接近200种随机宝物可供获取，每件宝物都会增强角斗士的五项基础属性。属性间相辅相成，搭配丰富，助你构筑独一无二的强大Build，体验持续成长的战斗快感</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063190/extras/6befe993b0f57cfcbdc43980992b0bab.webp?t=1763218319\" width=615 height=58 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063190/extras/d7e52baceff5c3e52c1cb7bfa2ce35e6.poster.avif?t=1763218319\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063190/extras/d7e52baceff5c3e52c1cb7bfa2ce35e6.webm?t=1763218319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063190/extras/d7e52baceff5c3e52c1cb7bfa2ce35e6.mp4?t=1763218319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>游戏分为三层竞技场，每层十天，每日可选择代表不同阵营出战。每次出战提升对应阵营声望，每积攒五点声望即可兑换该阵营专属宝物，任务选择直接影响成长路线</strong>",
